{`Blow-Fill-Seal & Form-Fill-Seal Solutions for Pharmaceuticals`}
"Unleashing the Power of BFS Technology: Aseptic Filling, Sterile Containers, and Unbreakable Packaging in a Single Step!"
Types of packaging
Eye-Drops

Our BFS (Blow-Fill-Seal) technology offers aseptic filling solutions for liquids, gels, ointments, and temperature-sensitive substances. Whether you need sterile single or multi-dose containers or require special features like Luer-Lock, our technology can handle it all in a single step. Rest assured, our BFS technology is fully certified and guarantees unbreakable packaging.
Eye-Drops
Best Primary Packaging for Ophthalmics: Sterile Blow-Fill-Seal Ampoules (0.25-0.6 ml) with No Preservatives. Resealable Multidoses (1-15 ml) with Tamper-Proof Closures. FDA-Certified, Anti-Counterfeiting Serialization, LDPE Options, Up to 12,000/hr Production."
Unlocking Optimal Results: Blow-Fill-Seal for Various Applications
